metadata.name: Tetrathemis Platyptera
metadata.description:
Tetrathemis Platyptera is a small dragonfly with yellow face and bluish green eyes. Its thorax and abdomen are yellow with broad black marks. Its wings are transparent, with fore-wings faintly and hind-wings broadly tinted with yellow in base.

This macro photograph was captured on Redmi Note 8 Pro with additional macro lens, handheld, manually focused. This is a single image and no manipulation or stacking is used to create this.

Creator: Febin Joe Varghese
Edition: 1/1
Collection Name: World of Small Creatures
